  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6487335">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6487335/" class="title-link">一部严谨的军事史著作</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6487335"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/80856381/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/80856381/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">[已注销]</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-12-31"
      class="main-meta">2013-12-31 18:40:04</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6487335_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看到有人拿这书和张洪涛的《国殇》比，我想说一句：你找错对象了。张洪涛的《国殇》是纪实文学，而这本书，是一部军事史著作。文学作品当然需要优美的文笔，因为只有这样才能将作者的感情更好地表达给读者；而史学作品需要的是严谨的例证，作者在写书中要尽可能的避免主观情绪...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6487335/#comments">(2回应)</a>
